{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lWritings from a lost cartographer...
\"},
                {\"text\":\"We managed to flee from the critters of these halls, and they aren't too keen on us being here. Unfortunately we lost the professor, but they weren't a great deal of help anyways.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Perhaps naming the site after their family could give a bit of honor to their name, but that's a side note before the main prize.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Nobody else could've picked a better spot to scour than this! Machinery, ore, sturdy tools, armor and enchantments? This ain't just any old mine! It's a Dwarven hall, belonging to one of the great clans!\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"I'm not much of a history buff, and the professor was yammering my ear off so I can't recall much. Planewalkers they said, dwarves that would travel between dimensions? Also heard they bickered about the way they traveled too. The specifics are lost on me.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Anyway, what matters here most is the treasure! Gold, emeralds, iron ore and more, this could make us a fortune if we invest in it right!\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"The red and black stones that make up the forge and throne are some fine bits of work. Could strip the walls clean with how much value we get out of them!\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Once we clean this place out, we could sell this to a couple of excavators and ask for a share of the profits.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Ancient Mines"]}
            }

{
          pages:[
              "[
                \"\",
                {\"text\":\"§lWritings from a lost adventurer...
\"},
                {\"text\":\"If anyone is reading this, I don't think I have much else to survive off of.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"This may be a bit of a shoddy obituary, but if anyone else is unfortunate enough to fall here, then maybe you won't be alone.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"My name is Jones, or Indy if you want to be buddies. At the time of writing, it's been three days since I've fallen down this god forsaken hole. \"},
                {\"text\":\"It was a blunder I made after trying to find shelter from the night, when I was returning from a local village.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"It wasn't a lot of goods, but you can go a long way with just a bit of bread. That unfortunately got soggy from the fall into this water pit, yet the fates found it funny to make it deep enough to cushion the fall. \"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Not sure if that was an act of mercy, because the sounds that had startled me at the foot of the hole now seem to echo throughout the... Mineshafts?\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"I think they're mineshafts... Anyway, I pray the fates also have some kind of salvation for me, because there's none I could see beyond the dim lit caverns. \"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"If you can find your way back up to the surface, and if for whatever reason you decide not to send for help (I wouldn't blame you), then plead for others to stay far away from here. This would be a nasty way to go, having your tomb be a place like this.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"P.S. If you are scared of insects, I think you won't have much luck here either. I heard a lot of skittering beyond the caverns from where I'm at, a bit of hissing too. Maybe bones? Be careful if you're a bit more liberal with your wellbeing.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:Unkown,
            display:{Lore:["Found in the Ancient Mines"]}
            }
